{"tid":798084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【現代鐵布衫】倫敦謀殺案太猖獗 有公司出防刺外套同奪刀手套","createTime":"2018-08-29T04:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T08:42:12.000Z","uid":44562,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6245253eaf036f7775d0521590b54e67094aed","tid":798084,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535458956_abfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535458956_abfc.jpg&h=33ad6470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535458956_b98f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535458956_b98f.jpg&h=19cbeb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦本年至今死於謀殺案的人數已達100人，街頭不時有途人被人用刀襲擊，有公司就乘勢推出防刺外套及手套，款式看上去和普通外衣無異，讓用家不幸要面對刀手時，可以多一分保障。<br />\n<br />\n特製保護衣物公司「Bladerunner」出售的防刺外套，售價為80英鎊（約809港元），就連T恤亦都可有防刺功能，每件賣約58英鎊（約585港元）。而奪刀手套就有分不同程度的防割級別，最便宜的賣8鎊（約80港元）、最貴的賣38鎊（約383港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有興趣 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baad825ceaf022fe53d9141e9558f8f6eaeeb5d4","tid":798084,"uid":36296,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:43:40.000Z","msg":"Blade runner <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597e5586cfe6b758a03dea00cf5f877ea5fb0b7e","tid":798084,"uid":67500,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"鬼佬唔識空手入白刃，渣ga"},{"pid":"7f1b0757dd347448d1ead682372aa060d5accaff","tid":798084,"uid":121580,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"597e5586cfe6b758a03dea00cf5f877ea5fb0b7e","tid":798084,"uid":67500,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"鬼佬唔識空手入白刃，渣ga"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"用手套可以接兩把刀<br />\n空手接白刃=一把"},{"pid":"e5910ba52bf2b7c47b14dba82acee0330c7ff7f0","tid":798084,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:05:32.000Z","msg":"幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我有靈犀一指就得"},{"pid":"0f8abdc3fcac5cc04375df8036c024d3dc6808bd","tid":798084,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"幾時要進行刀具管制<br />\nd刀咁危險殺得死人"},{"pid":"a3cf7db1bc574e4f70302b4e7101c7adfeeaf49d","tid":798084,"uid":141606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"防割手套不嬲都有<br />\n但係市面上賣嘅<br />\n就算去到lv 5都好<br />\n都只係防到手揸嗰一下<br />\n佢把刀向前/後一拉<br />\n或者有齒嘅<br />\n都係會穿<br />\n<br />\n除非係工業用好似太空人手套嗰啲咁"},{"pid":"cb12e6167a83db99f9f95105005a174be31e10ce","tid":798084,"uid":44898,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"防刺外套,背心淘寶之前大把<br />\n咩質地都有,又平又正<br />\n依家唔知有無得賣啦<br />\n防割手套就更加多<br />\n就算拖刀都唔爆口"},{"pid":"91805a3bbcea45204048ef096da3ad7f072c4138","tid":798084,"uid":197337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:26:08.000Z","msg":"其實美國人出街可唔可以着避彈衣??"},{"pid":"455bfa28983248df1d561e20d09038c3d8b20b02","tid":798084,"uid":71218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cb12e6167a83db99f9f95105005a174be31e10ce","tid":798084,"uid":44898,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"防刺外套,背心淘寶之前大把<br />\n咩質地都有,又平又正<br />\n依家唔知有無得賣啦<br />\n防割手套就更加多<br />\n就算拖刀都唔爆口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"你不如試下買件番黎再叫FD刺你一刀睇下穿唔穿,包你一刺成名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c908b753d58e0d128bd59d10793e877a8b4a9c88","tid":798084,"uid":197337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"455bfa28983248df1d561e20d09038c3d8b20b02","tid":798084,"uid":71218,"l